0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:32:05.000Z","msg":"唔使理，一個月唔好先算"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:35:15.000Z","msg":"咁再等下添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果唔口痕搞佢的話 都係突少少<br />\n如果搞佢/食野果陣會漲大左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n粒野起左兩個禮拜<br />\n唯有等多一頭半個月睇下點先算"},{"pid":"31ea675881fe2f9e0885f553fe84203522f70978","tid":1304021,"uid":94950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5da8a38630996c62ea336adfc445eec9e6ee90ee","tid":1304021,"uid":127041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c279e7470639a83002babf5045fbe29a680961c","tid":1304021,"uid":94950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:26:50.000Z","msg":"如果係mucocele，多數幾星期至幾個月就會消"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:29:59.000Z","msg":"上網睇話唔會自己好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n極多數都要做手術<br />\n知唔知做手術要幾錢<br />\n冇儲開錢驚要洗幾皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:37:39.000Z","msg":"之前睇過口腔科醫生，佢話手術大概半個鐘做完，around 12k。不過做完唔一定保證可以切左條口水線，所以考慮到最後我都冇做到，過左3個月之後就自己消左。<br />\n我既建議係，如果你大把錢既就做手術試下都可以。<br />\n如果你粒口水瘡唔係話好痛既話，你可以再觀察下先，可能幾個星期就冇左都唔定。"},{"pid":"90a10f1b6c7ada1850835c1d7deae90ea9c36faa","tid":1304021,"uid":127041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"31ea675881fe2f9e0885f553fe84203522f70978","tid":1304021,"uid":94950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5da8a38630996c62ea336adfc445eec9e6ee90ee","tid":1304021,"uid":127041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c279e7470639a83002babf5045fbe29a680961c","tid":1304021,"uid":94950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:26:50.000Z","msg":"如果係mucocele，多數幾星期至幾個月就會消"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:29:59.000Z","msg":"上網睇話唔會自己好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n極多數都要做手術<br />\n知唔知做手術要幾錢<br />\n冇儲開錢驚要洗幾皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:37:39.000Z","msg":"之前睇過口腔科醫生，佢話手術大概半個鐘做完，around 12k。不過做完唔一定保證可以切左條口水線，所以考慮到最後我都冇做到，過左3個月之後就自己消左。<br />\n我既建議係，如果你大把錢既就做手術試下都可以。<br />\n如果你粒口水瘡唔係話好痛既話，你可以再觀察下先，可能幾個星期就冇左都唔定。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:41:48.000Z","msg":"唔搞佢又真係唔痛既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯有再等下睇下點<br />\n反正應該唔死的人 又唔影響外觀<br />\n<br />\n上網睇見到大陸仔玩人體脫水毒死左粒野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dbba32f35ea3be4af97ad161ddb56b939041f6a","tid":1304021,"uid":127041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:37:40.000Z","msg":"好想吉穿佢睇下有冇野流出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}